NoData value and data type for Chelsa variables.

Source: R/data.R
nodata_chelsa.Rd

A dataset with the nodata value and data type for each climatic variable provided in Chelsa. The variables are as follows:

nodata_chelsa

Format

nodata_chelsa

A data frame with 25 rows and 5 variables:

var

Climatic variable

month

Month of the year

dtype

Data type

nodata

NoData value

Source

https://chelsa-climate.org/
